, T. Kumata leg. (genitalia slide no. OPU-SK486). Paratypes Host. 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Tilia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tilia japonica" order="Malvales" pageId="6" pageNumber="133" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="japonica">Tilia japonica</taxonomicName>
